data.description: **ASSUMABLE VA LOAN @ 3.125% & SELLER OFFERING 2/1 BUYDOWN OR UP TO $8,000 IN CLOSING COSTS!** Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by the charming curb appeal of this spacious home, featuring lush landscaping, and a welcoming front porch. Inside, the open and airy living spaces are designed for modern living while embracing a sense of coziness and warmth. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, boasting stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, and a center island, perfect for preparing family meals or entertaining guests. The adjacent dining area flows seamlessly into the spacious living room, creating an ideal space for gatherings and relaxation. This home's three bedrooms include a master suite, complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring a upgraded vanity, soaking tub, and shower. The additional bedrooms provide space for family, guests, or the flexibility to create a home office or hobby room. Step outside to discover the expansive backyard, a private oasis for outdoor living. The screened lanai is perfect for al fresco dining, while the lush lawn offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening.
